Package model

Class Summary
Board The Board class is a mutable class.
Game  
Move The Move class is an immutable class.
MoveHistoryObject The MoveHistoryObject class is an immutable class.
MoveValidation The MoveValidation class is used to gather information about the available moves that a given board has.
Piece The Piece class is a mutable class.
PlayerClock The PlayerClock keeps track of how much time a player has left on his game clock.
Square The Square class is an immutable class.
 

Enum Summary
ChessEvent The ChessEvent enum represents the different event types that can be thrown throughout the Antichess game.
PieceType The PieceType enum represents 8 different types of chess pieces: Pawn, Rook, Queen, King, Bishop, Knight, AntiKing, Empty, and Passant
 

Exception Summary
InvalidBoardStringException This exception is thrown when an invalid string is trying to be converted into a Board.
InvalidMoveStringException This exception is thrown when an invalid string is trying to be converted into a Move.
InvalidSquareStringException This exception is thrown when an invalid string is trying to be converted into a Square.
